$ ./appme --help           
usage: appme [-h] [--role ROLE] [--year YEAR] [--dry_run] company friendly

positional arguments:
  company          what company one is applying for
  friendly         a name you can use in the cover letter

options:
  -h, --help       show this help message and exit
  --role, -r ROLE  title of position
  --year, -y YEAR  what year the role is for, assumes for next year
  --dry_run


notes:

must use these sentinels in template, or fork the repo and change it...

COMPANY_SENTINEL = "@@REPLACE@WITH@COMPANY@NAME@@"
ROLE_SENTINEL = "@REPLACE@WITH@ROLE@@"